Document: Slider
Path: godot/classes/class_slider.rst
Summary: This section details the properties of the Slider node in Godot Engine.

Properties:
* editable (bool): If true, the slider can be edited. Default: true.
* focus_mode (FocusMode): The focus mode of the control. Default: 2 (overrides Control.focus_mode).
* scrollable (bool): If true, the slider can be scrolled. Default: true.
* step (float): The step value for the slider. Default: 1.0 (overrides Range.step).
* tick_count (int): The number of ticks to display on the slider. Default: 0.
* ticks_on_borders (bool): If true, ticks will be displayed on the borders of the slider. Default: false.
* ticks_position (TickPosition): The position of the ticks on the slider. Default: 0.
