Path: godot/classes/class_slider.rst
Summary: Describes the properties of the Slider node in Godot Engine, including its editability, scrollability, tick marks, and tick positions.

Property Descriptions
editable (bool): If true, the slider can be interacted with. If false, the value can be changed only by code.
  Method: set_editable(value: bool)
  Method: is_editable() → bool

scrollable (bool): If true, the value can be changed using the mouse wheel.
  Method: set_scrollable(value: bool)
  Method: is_scrollable() → bool

tick_count (int): Number of ticks displayed on the slider, including border ticks. Ticks are uniformly-distributed value markers.
  Method: set_ticks(value: int)
  Method: get_ticks() → int

ticks_on_borders (bool): If true, the slider will display ticks for minimum and maximum values.
  Method: set_ticks_on_borders(value: bool)
  Method: get_ticks_on_borders() → bool

ticks_position (TickPosition): Sets the position of the ticks. See TickPosition for details.
  Method: set_ticks_position(value: TickPosition)
  Method: get_ticks_position() → TickPosition
---CHUNK---
Document: Slider
Path: godot/classes/class_slider.rst
Summary: Describes the theme properties for the Slider node, including constants, icons, and styles.

Theme Property Descriptions:
- center_grabber (int): Boolean constant. If 1, the grabber texture size will be ignored and it will fit within slider's bounds based only on its center position. Default: 0
- grabber_offset (int): Vertical or horizontal offset of the grabber. Default: 0
- tick_offset (int): Vertical or horizontal offset of the ticks. The offset is reversed for top or left ticks. Default: 0
- grabber (Texture2D): The texture for the grabber (the draggable element).
- grabber_disabled (Texture2D): The texture for the grabber when it's disabled.
- grabber_highlight (Texture2D): The texture for the grabber when it's focused.
- tick (Texture2D): The texture for the ticks, visible when tick_count is greater than 0.
- grabber_area (StyleBox): The background of the area to the left or bottom of the grabber.
- grabber_area_highlight (StyleBox): The background of the area to the left or bottom of the grabber that displays when it's being hovered or focused.
- slider (StyleBox): The background for the whole slider. Affects the height or width of the grabber_area.